hopobject.body: Where do you study? alpha fuel xt reviews Four engine options are available the 95hp 1.4-litre petrol (5-seat only) the 105hp 0.9 TwinAir petrol the 85hp 1.3 MultiJet (also available with the Dualogic automatic transmission) and the 105hp 1.6-litre MultiJet. There are nine different exterior colours to choose from plus a variety of contrasting roof and mirror colour combinations. To complete the look there is also a range of alloy wheels in different sizes to choose from.
